Notification Viewer
-------------------

This add-on for Mozilla Thunderbird identifies and displays the status of awaiting
and received notifications for messages sent with notifications requests.
Identified notifications are:
* DSN (Delivery Status Notification)
* MDN (Message Disposition Notification)

This add-on is written in XUL and JavaScript.

DIRSIM - Marine Nationale
Trustedbird/Milimail project
